Port/Signal     Bitwidth    Direction   Destination                 Description
HBREQ           1           output      Arbiter                     multi master, Transfer request
HGRANT          1           input                                   multi master, Transfer grant
HADDR           32          output      Decoder,Slave
HBURST          3           output      Slave
HNONSEC         1           output      Decoder,Slave
HEXCL           1           output      Exclusive Access Monitor
HMASTER         N           output      Exclusive Access Monitor    #exclusive threads
HMASTLOCK       1           output      Arbiter,Slave               multi master, Transfer not preemptible
HPROT           7           output      Slave
HSIZE           3           output      Slave
HTRANS          2           output      Slave
HWRITE          1           output      Slave
HWRITE          N           output      Slave                       8,16,32,64,128,256,512,1024 bit

